description: This file defines a Dart class 'Patient' used in a healthcare management system front-end. It models patient data including fields like id, userId, email, fullName, age, medicalHistory, and allergies, along with methods for JSON serialization and deserialization.

classes.name: Patient
classes.description: A data model representing a patient with personal and medical information.
